Applications of Artificial Intelligence
Artificial Intelligence is widely used across various industries:
Healthcare (disease diagnosis, medical imaging)
Finance (fraud detection, algorithmic trading)
Transportation (autonomous vehicles)
Education (personalized learning systems)
Despite its benefits, AI also presents challenges such as data privacy concerns, bias in algorithms, and ethical considerations.

