Conclusion
Artificial Intelligence continues to evolve rapidly and plays a crucial role in modern technology. As AI systems become more advanced, responsible development and deployment are essential to ensure fairness, transparency, and accountability.
Future research in AI focuses on improving interpretability, robustness, and alignment with human values.
